      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="Maintain the system tables that control product pricing.  ​These tables are usually valid for long time periods (e.g., one year).​&#10;Maintain tables for list pricing (i.e., the price displayed on the published price list).​ Maintain additional tables for special pricing either for particular customers or for special product lines.​​"/>
